*Godine* su se prolazile, a on je ostao isti. (The years were passing by, but he remained the same.)

*Godinama* se trudio da postigne svoje ciljeve. (He had been striving for years to achieve his goals.)

*Godinu* dana se nije videla njena porodica. (Her family had not been seen for a year.)

*Godišnje* su se menjale njene navike. (Her habits were changing yearly.)

Njegove *godine* su ga učinile mudrijim. (His years made him wiser.)

Njena *godina* je protekla u učenju. (Her year was spent in learning.)

Najteža *godina* je bila ispred njega. (The hardest year was ahead of him.)